channel.title: Panini on Tiny Tavern
channel.description: Recent content in Panini on Tiny Tavern

item.title: Grilled Chicken Panini
item.description: This delicious panini is made with tender chicken breast, sweet corn, green peppers, and cheddar cheese sandwiched between two slices of multigrain bread.

item.title: Ham Panini
item.description: This delicious panini is made with ham, spinach, and cheddar cheese sandwiched between two slices of multigrain bread.

item.title: Jalapeño Turkey Bacon Panini
item.description: This delicious panini is made with turkey bacon, jalapeño, spinach, mushroom, and cheddar cheese sandwiched between two slices of multigrain bread.

item.title: The Amazing Vegetarian Panini
item.description: This delicious panini is made with spinach, tomato, pineapple, and cheddar cheese sandwiched between two slices of multigrain bread.

item.title: TT's Talked About Panini
item.description: This delicious panini is made with turkey bacon, jalapeño, bell pepper, pineapple, and cheddar cheese sandwiched between two slices of multigrain bread.
